lead_paragraph: Marreese Speights had 18 points and Nick Calathes had 16 points, 5 rebounds and 5 assists as Florida (22-11) ended a four-game skid with a 73-49 victory over San Diego State (20-13) in Gainesville during the first round of the National Invitation Tournament. ... A. D. Vassallo made 11 of 14 field-goal tries and had 27 points in 25 minutes as Virginia Tech (20-13) won, 94-62, against Morgan State (22-11) in Blacksburg, Va.
